{"tid":1535991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太子被打市民入！！！","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:37:58.000Z","uid":310858,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d6d264f96377704ad93729d322820ca167ec90","tid":1535991,"uid":310858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ftawsv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ftawsv.png&h=315943d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心急呀！！！！！！！！求下你哋快d出黎！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"d8873877b88066df9d0023b554af694800eaaac4","tid":1535991,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5a15e3cc35590f8cf0d9a6a6dc7d4d123c8cabd","tid":1535991,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:16:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaf1bd45ee6dbfc8146578d74fc578189c295b43","tid":1535991,"uid":68226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"以前曾經說過，香港現在的亂局，可以透過法律和政治解決。<br />\n<br />\n若有人因近來的暴力事件而感到不安，受到情緒困擾，其實可以向香港現任特首、警務處處長和港鐵公司作出民事索償。<br />\n<br />\n如有人在乘搭港鐵時侯遇到襲擊、恐嚇，或因乘搭港鐵而身處突如其來的暴力環境，因此而身體受損或情緒受到衝擊，也可以向港鐵公司循民事途徑索取賠償。<br />\n<br />\n香港的訴訟費用非常昂貴，但循小額錢債審裁處申索賠償，若索取賠償金額不超過5千元，遞交申索書的費用僅20元，而且所有事情皆可自行處理，不必另聘律師。<br />\n<br />\n假如有一百萬市民向警務處處長提出申索，每人要求索賠5千元，累積索賠金額便達到50億元。<br />\n<br />\n這類小額錢債官司過程簡單，每個人都可以自行處理。<br />\n<br />\n今天便有一單市民向警務處處長索賠5千元的例子，將會對香港的亂局起到一定的積極作用。<br />\n<br />\n本文不是唆擺任何人對某些人作出不合理的訴訟，而是希望情緒受困擾的朋友知道如何處理一些事情，對香港好，也對自己好。"},{"pid":"a784b61e2c75eb8c1dbacbada35addcb06a09321","tid":1535991,"uid":276693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c5363cd808c63871dcb4fd7678e2599e6d51762","tid":1535991,"uid":155518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d21ccccd15ed7182719cdb70826db19ac06a42","tid":1535991,"uid":197228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:29:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0777302829bdfa69597f590f3e41f40909342bb","tid":1535991,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e270e0330023b5e92b48b848b1905098bf2a858","tid":1535991,"uid":13343,"like":0,"disli